00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,030
and thought

291
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,220
it was pretty awesome.

292
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,850
So we discussed and thought

293
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,240
that not only could we pick up girls,

294
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,640
we could also
start classes and make money.

295
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,720
So I quickly put together
some simple materials,

296
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,520
and was getting ready for class.

297
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,920
Then he disappeared.

298
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,390
Later I heard

299
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,320
he scammed the daughter of a mob boss.

300
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,570
They were going to chop off his legs,

301
00:14:55,570 --> 00:14:56,410
so he ran away.

302
00:14:57,150 --> 00:14:57,870
About

303
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,480
less than 2 years later,

304
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,660
he showed up again.

305
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,030
He got plastic surgery

306
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,240
and got a Pazion passport.

307
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,500
He became a foreigner.

308
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,550
Then he told me that

309
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,150
in Pazion,

310
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,270
he started a new e-commerce platform.

311
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:12,200
When I got there,

312
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:16,680
I realized it was just
old wine in a new bottle.

313
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:19,040
We didn't even need to meet one-on-one.

314
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:21,520
As long as we set up
our online personas

315
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,630
and keep chatting
to build an emotional connection,

316
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:24,760
we could make money.

317
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,700
In his words, it's like

318
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,510
bringing a pig into a pigpen,

319
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,910
waiting for it to get fat,

320
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:32,970
and then slaughtering it.

321
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,810
He said it's called

322
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:36,840
a pig-butchering scam.

323
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,580
How do you usually contact Lin Huosheng?

324
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,200
To be honest,

325
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,920
to me, he really is

326
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,670
very elusive.

327
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:55,720
He's the one who always contacts me first.

328
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,200
Was Jian Leilei your first case?

329
00:16:15,670 --> 00:16:16,360
I guess

330
00:16:16,510 --> 00:16:17,600
you could say so.

331
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:19,600
That day,

332
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:22,000
I happened to be on duty.

333
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,750
Do you know what my first case was

334
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,880
when I joined the Special Crimes Unit?

335
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,440
A female college student
who just graduated

336
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,970
was scammed out of 150,000.

337
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:39,730
Right in front of me,

338
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,570
she jumped off a bridge.

339
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:43,790
Before she died,

340
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:45,600
she even called the man who scammed her

341
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,800
to ask if he loved her.

342
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,030
Pigs.

343
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:54,670
In the eyes of those scammers,

344
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:56,400
they don't even deserve a name.

345
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:58,720
Because of this,

346
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,840
we have to be calmer and colder

347
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,590
than those scammers.

348
00:17:06,569 --> 00:17:12,990
[Dongchuan Public Security Department]

349
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:07,970
Understood.

350
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:11,790
OK.

351
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:12,790
Let's go

352
00:17:12,869 --> 00:17:14,000
interrogate Xia Yi.

353
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,000
Any new progress on the clues

354
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,930
provided by Yan Ling and Lu Yifeng?

355
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,240
Um, well,

356
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,410
Yu Kexin said

357
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:33,380
Xia Yi might return to the country
next week.

358
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:34,310
OK.

359
00:17:39,370 --> 00:17:41,970
Right, I said it wouldn't be
until next week...

360
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,040
[Pazion:
Border Area of ​​Koramanrat Province]

361
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:11,640
Keep up.

362
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,270
I'm keeping up.

363
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,310
Can you keep up?

364
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,640
If you dawdle any longer,

365
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,110
you'll miss your boat tonight.

366
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:19,910
Don't worry. I have you, don't I?

367
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:36,240
Is Master Bei

368
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,900
coming back with you tonight?

369
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:39,440
Yes. I've told you so many times.

370
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,700
Why do you keep asking?

371
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:43,270
Please let me go.

372
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:44,920
I'm just worried
you're only concerned about Master Bei

373
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:47,360
and forget the bracelet
I asked you to buy for me.

374
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:48,350
Don't worry.

375
00:18:48,350 --> 00:18:50,150
I'll put it on you when I get back.

376
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,720
Let me go!

377
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:55,450
Hello.

378
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:56,270
Baby,

379
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:59,480
I didn't reply these two days
because I was sick.

380
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:09,440
Darling,

381
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,350
if we make money from this investment,

382
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,770
I can marry you.

383
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:13,610
Thank you for

384
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:16,310
helping me raise enough betrothal money
for my mom.

385
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:18,160
Let me go! Let me go!

386
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,590
Let me go!

387
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:22,440
Trying to escape?

388
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,170
How dare you!

389
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,460
Realize your mistake?

390
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,510
Stop it!

391
00:19:25,550 --> 00:19:26,110
Master Bei.

392
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,590
Master Bei, I'm sorry.

393
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:30,440
I'll never try to run again.
I know I was wrong.

394
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,000
Tell them to stop hitting me.

395
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,100
During your chats,

396
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:36,510
will you still ask them
to call the police for you?

397
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,720
No more calling the police.

398
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:40,550
I won't call the police anymore.

399
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,030
Master Bei.

400
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:42,600
Sir,

401
00:19:42,830 --> 00:19:44,690
Master Bei said we're ready to go.

402
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,440
Got it.

403
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,340
Master Bei.

404
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:57,560
Brother.

405
00:20:06,350 --> 00:20:07,220
Good girl.

406
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,590
Just this once.

407
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:10,420
OK, OK.

408
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:12,680
It hurts a lot to be beaten, doesn't it?

409
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:15,460
I'll help you
not to make mistakes again, OK?

410
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,550
OK, OK.

411
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,750
Thank you, Master Bei.

412
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,610
-Thank you, Master Bei.
-Be good.

413
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:45,010
This is the price of talking nonsense.

414
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,310
Don't think you can mess around

415
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:51,480
just because I'll be away for a few days!

416
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:52,230
Get to work!

417
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:39,070
[School of Atmospheric & Oceanic Sciences,
Lihai University of Science & Technology]

418
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:31,580
Hello, Ms. Yan.

419
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:35,960
It's me.

420
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,970
Did Officer Li contact you later?

421
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:43,830
[Lihai Meteorology]

422
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:39,920
No.

423
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,590
After that Ouyang got arrested,

424
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,120
he didn't contact me again.

425
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:47,160
What did Officer Li say about the video?

426
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:49,730
He said it will be strictly sealed off,

427
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,070
but...

428
00:21:51,260 --> 00:21:56,070
[Lihai Meteorology]

429
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:54,070
It's just...

430
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:56,070
I-I heard those bastards say

431
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:58,160
they might package the video

432
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,680
and sell it to porn sites.

433
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,840
B-But it's just a possibility.

434
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:02,920
They couldn't have

435
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,380
had the time to do all that.

436
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,290
Did you contact Fang Fang?

437
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:09,510
No.

438
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:12,790
I'm sorry.

439
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,880
Why are you saying sorry?

440
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,750
This is what I wanted to do.

441
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,550
Even if it wasn't for you

442
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:20,510
or Leilei,

443
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:21,960
just as a man,

444
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,480
I couldn't just watch those scumbags

445
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:24,880
exploit women like that.

446
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:25,880
Lu.

447
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:27,440
Lu?

448
00:22:27,690 --> 00:22:32,260
[Lihai Meteorology]

449
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,680
Alright, don't overthink it.

450
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,740
I have things to do.

451
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:31,400
Bye.

452
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:39,200
Dr. Luo.

453
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,760
Your package.

454
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:41,760
Thank you.

455
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:44,890
Are you busy today?

456
00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:46,030
Not bad.

457
00:22:46,590 --> 00:22:47,070
Not bad.

458
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:51,680
Hello?

459
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,090
I'll be right there.

460
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,830
Jiale! Jiale!

461
00:23:32,110 --> 00:23:33,370
Fasten your seatbelt.

462
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,190
[Incoming call: Dr. Luo Liang]

463
00:23:46,070 --> 00:23:47,400
Not answering the call?

464
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,180
[Incoming call: Dr. Luo Liang]

465
00:23:51,210 --> 00:23:53,830
[Dr. Luo Liang]

466
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:53,600
Hello?

467
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:55,480
Ms. Yan.

468
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,970
I received the clothes,

469
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,660
but there's a problem.

470
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:03,270
What problem?

471
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,260
I was wondering

472
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:08,310
why you didn't just give them to me

473
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:09,370
in person instead.

474
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:14,200
I've been quite busy with work lately.

475
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:17,400
Does that mean
Jiale hasn't been eating properly again?

476
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:19,350
I recently saw a tutorial
for making cold rice noodles.

477
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,270
It requires washing the dough.

478
00:24:20,270 --> 00:24:21,330
I want to practice.

479
00:24:21,620 --> 00:24:23,160
Whenever you and Jiale have time—

480
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,440
I'm sorry, Dr. Luo.

481
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:26,740
It's almost the end of the term.

482
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:28,770
Jiale and I are really busy.

483
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:31,480
I see.

484
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:34,140
I-I'm driving right now.

485
00:24:34,140 --> 00:24:35,120
I'll hang up now.

486
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:37,110
OK, bye.

487
00:24:37,290 --> 00:24:38,230
[Dr. Luo Liang]

488
00:24:38,340 --> 00:24:39,230
[Missed call: Dr. Luo Liang]

489
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,880
What happened between you two?

490
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:51,880
What do you mean?

491
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,820
Dr. Luo just helped you

492
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,160
and lent you clothes.

493
00:24:57,350 --> 00:24:58,080
But just now,

494
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,720
you talked to him on the phone

495
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:01,200
like it was a scam call.

496
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,710
I don't think I was that rude.

497
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:05,190
You were.

498
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,850
You didn't treat him like this before.

499
00:25:39,750 --> 00:25:40,610
Oh my goodness.

500
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,350
I just went to the restroom

501
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:44,080
and saw that Madam Chen is back.

502
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:46,240
You mean the hypochondriac?

503
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:46,830
Yes, her.

504
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,720
Every time, she brings a suitcase

505
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:51,160
full of scans and medical records.

506
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:54,160
And she always insists that
I read them from beginning to end.

507
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,220
Every single time.

508
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:56,720
She alone can drive

509
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,240
the other waiting patients crazy.

510
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,970
I've been working all morning,

511
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,150
and I've only seen 8 patients.

512
00:26:02,150 --> 00:26:03,210
If she comes again,

513
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:06,330
how am I supposed to
see my other patients?

514
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,900
Why don't you take a break?

515
00:26:09,060 --> 00:26:10,150
I'll cover for you.

516
00:26:12,650 --> 00:26:14,020
I love a challenge.

517
00:26:15,590 --> 00:26:16,030
OK.

518
00:26:16,230 --> 00:26:16,830
Thanks.

519
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:36,480
Where are we?

520
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,200
Should be there soon.

521
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,130
We've passed the boundary marker.

522
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:05,290
Here.

523
00:27:15,590 --> 00:27:16,000
Here.

524
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:27,530
Brother!

525
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:28,640
Here.

526
00:27:39,830 --> 00:27:42,310
He Dayong! He Xiaobing! Lin Huosheng!

527
00:27:42,610 --> 00:27:43,790
How did the word get out?

528
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:45,250
We are Lihai Police!

529
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,550
Damn that Yu Kexin.

530
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:49,280
You are suspected of a crime
and are surrounded!

531
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:50,920
Drop your weapons

532
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,170
and surrender!

533
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,780
It's your only way out!

534
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:54,670
Fire!

535
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:55,400
Fire!

536
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:05,960
Fire!

537
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:07,820
Fire! Fire!

538
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:15,840
Watch out!

539
00:28:19,950 --> 00:28:21,300
Pudge, are you OK?

540
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,530
The bullet hit his right shoulder blade.

541
00:28:27,530 --> 00:28:28,640
It's not a penetrating injury.

542
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:30,300
He is not in immediate danger.

543
00:28:31,550 --> 00:28:32,200
Thank you.

544
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:41,650
You're leaving
just because the doctor has left?

545
00:28:41,760 --> 00:28:43,160
You're so cold-blooded.

546
00:28:44,510 --> 00:28:45,350
I told you to sit out

547
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,070
the arrest operation,

548
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:47,400
but you wouldn't listen.

549
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,530
With your physique,

550
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:50,830
you're defintely
not suited for field duty.

551
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:51,310
What?

552
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,080
Here.

553
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,660
Careful.

554
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,450
So what if I'm not suited?

555
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:03,000
At least I'm thick enough.

556
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,530
If it were someone else,

557
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:08,100
the bullet would have
gone through them and hit you.

558
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,400
You desk officers

559
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,750
have no combat experience

560
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,280
and don't know your limits.

561
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:14,800
Does it hurt?

562
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:18,930
A little,
now that the anesthesia is wearing off.

563
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:27,480
Thank you.

564
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,920
I said, "Thank you."

565
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,570
You're welcome.

566
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,400
Paw Patrol,

567
00:29:39,790 --> 00:29:40,240
you can't

568
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:41,790
just say thanks.

569
00:29:43,070 --> 00:29:44,800
You have to take actual action.

570
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:49,480
What action?

571
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:06,440
Don't push your luck.

572
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:10,610
Lin Huosheng,

573
00:30:12,150 --> 00:30:13,480
let me interrogate him.

574
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,660
Focus on your recovery

575
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:20,600
and return to the team soon.

576
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:24,770
